data.name: trainerItemsInfo_lbl.Text
data.value: Here, you can set your trainers' items. You can add and/or remove them here. You can only have a maximum of 8 items per trainer (per Pokémon Essentials Limitation) Use the buttons below or click the Add button to add your own item.

data.name: aboutInfo_lbl.Text
data.value: The EASY Way to Build a Team. This tool is free and open-source. It is built so you can build your own teams in the Pokemon Essentials game engine! I always have found the tools that come with essentials to be pretty bad, so I am building my own custom tools to make it easier!
